Computer.name: DEC Internal Workstation Joan
Computer.file: Steve: You hear what John did? Joan: No, tell me. Steve: IT guy caught him using the same password for a couple months now. Joan: Oh, he's pretty strict about changing those. Steve: yeah Steve: Anyway, all John did was stick a 2 on the end. Joan: That's one way to remember at least. Steve: wym? Joan: Isn't that what we all do?
